Retrieve shipping order 
  GET /shippingOrder/{id}?fields=...&{filtering} 
Description 
This operation retrieves a shipping order entity. 
Attribute selection is enabled for all first level attributes. 
Filtering on sub-resources may be available depending on the compliance level supported by an implementation. 

